<!-- Aboutus Section Begin -->
<section class="aboutus-section spad">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="aboutus-page-text">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xl-9 col-lg-10 m-auto">
          <div class="section-title">
            <h2>Who we Are & What We Do</h2>
            <p>
              Fightrix Club is a dynamic combat sports community dedicated to empowering individuals through Muay Thai, MMA, kickboxing, and boxing training. We focus on providing accessible opportunities for underprivileged and differently-abled children, as well as supporting those overcoming addiction and mental health challenges!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <%= image_tag asset_path("about-us.jpg") %>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <div class="about-us">
            <h4>ABOUT US</h4>

            <p>
              Welcome to Fightrix Club, a proud and dynamic branch of the Combat Sports Welfare Society—The Matrix, Where Fighters Are Forged. At Fightrix, we believe in the transformative power of combat sports—not only as a means to physical fitness but as a tool to empower individuals and communities. Our club offers world-class training in Muay Thai, MMA, kickboxing, and boxing, designed for people of all skill levels, from beginners to seasoned athletes.
            </p>

            <p>
              As a proud initiative of the Combate Sports Welfare Society, we’re committed to breaking down barriers so underprivileged and differently-abled children can access the training, resources, and support they deserve. Our mission goes beyond fitness—we’re tackling real social challenges like drug addiction and mental health struggles by providing rehabilitation through combat sports and wellness programs.
            </p>

            <p>
              We understand that mental wellness and physical strength are closely intertwined. At Fightrix, we provide a safe space for people recovering from addiction, offering them a path to rebuild their lives through discipline, resilience, and focus. Through our partnership with the Combate Sports Welfare Society, we reach out to those in need of social support, be it recovering addicts, underprivileged communities, or people facing life’s toughest challenges.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <div class="about-quality">
            <h4>OUR QUALITY</h4>
            <p>
              Fightrix is more than just a training ground for fighters—it's a movement. We’re building a supportive, inclusive community where people can grow stronger in both body and mind.
            </p>

            <ul>
              <li>
                <i class="fa fa-check-circle-o"></i>
                Dynamic branch of the Combat Sports Welfare Society — part of a larger movement ("The Matrix, Where Fighters Are Forged").
              </li>
              <li>
                <i class="fa fa-check-circle-o"></i>
                Supportive and inclusive environment focused on both physical and mental growth.
              </li>
              <li>
                <i class="fa fa-check-circle-o"></i>
                Inclusive for all skill levels — from beginners to experienced athletes.
              </li>
              <li>
                <i class="fa fa-check-circle-o"></i>
                Open to everyone, including differently-abled individuals and underprivileged youth.
              </li>
              <li>
                <i class="fa fa-check-circle-o"></i>
                Rehabilitation through fitness — using structure, discipline, and resilience from combat sports.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<!-- Aboutus Section End -->

<!-- Our Vision Section Begin -->
<section class="aboutus-section spad pt-5">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="aboutus-page-text">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col">
          <div class="about-us">
            <h4>OUR VISION</h4>

            <p>
              At Fightrix Club, our vision is to lead the combat sports community—not just by shaping champions in the ring, but by empowering lives beyond it. We’re building a space where people from all backgrounds can come together to train, grow, and strengthen themselves physically, mentally, and emotionally.
            </p>

            <p>
              As a proud arm of the Combate Sports Welfare Society, we’re dedicated to making combat sports accessible to everyone. Our mission especially focuses on underprivileged and differently-abled children who may not otherwise have these opportunities. We also support individuals recovering from addiction and mental health struggles, using combat sports as a powerful tool for rehabilitation and transformation.
            </p>

            <p>
              We envision a future where combat sports foster confidence, discipline, resilience, and unity. Our goal is to cultivate not only skilled athletes but also empowered individuals—equipped to face life’s challenges and uplift their communities. Through sponsorships, inclusive programs, and a commitment to social impact, Fightrix stands as a force for both personal and societal change.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<!-- Our Vision Section End -->

<!-- Brand Vision Section Begin -->
<section class="aboutus-section spad pt-5">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="aboutus-page-text">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col">
          <div class="about-us">
            <h4>BRAND VISION</h4>

            <p>
              At Fightrix, our brand is built on more than just combat sports excellence—it represents strength, resilience, inclusivity, and meaningful social change. We strive to be known as a community that not only shapes champions in the arena but also empowers individuals to unlock their full potential, both mentally and physically.
            </p>

            <p>
              Our mission reaches far beyond the gym. We're deeply committed to supporting those in need of rehabilitation and healing. Through our outreach and social initiatives, we combat drug addiction, raise awareness around mental health, and offer a path to recovery and personal transformation through the discipline of combat sports.
            </p>

            <p>
              Fightrix stands for empowerment—especially for those who have been overlooked or marginalized. Our goal is to establish a trusted, impactful brand known for excellence, inclusivity, and community-driven values. We’re here to promote strength of body, clarity of mind, and the growth of individuals who rise above their challenges through focus, determination, and the unifying power of sport.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
